,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T06:33:34.000Z","msg":"好簡單，你有冇見過有人得票數輸成幾街<br />\n個樣仲可以咁得戚?"},{"pid":"763e76ff1c05268257685cb1604b1347ccad5e2a","tid":919524,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T06:33:54.000Z","msg":"成個so call 泛民都係鬼<br />\n全部都小罵大幫忙"},{"pid":"0b6502366ef1fe8d014b11a923e8264c2419a108","tid":919524,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T06:35:07.000Z","msg":"夠唔夠呢道鬼?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2017年6月17日，沙中線8.47億追加撥款以6票之差獲得通過，10名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2017/06/17/162225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F162225&d=7QB4h8mQ1QBJp1iJ1m8od5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=c8161aa0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2017/06/17/162225</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年3月22日，立法會審議 1131億臨時撥款，在全體泛民議員缺席下，議案只花兩分鐘，由不足十名建制派議員在不記名投票下贊成通過。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180322/bkn-20180322090338992-0322_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180322%2Fbkn-20180322090338992-0322_00822_001.html&d=7QB4h8mQ1QBJp1iJ1m8od5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=9d72557b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180322/bkn-20180322090338992-0322_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年5月26日，工務小組審議17.85億元朗行人天橋撥款，議案以3票之差獲得通過，5名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/fc/pwsc/results/v201805261.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr17-18%2Fchinese%2Ffc%2Fpwsc%2Fresults%2Fv201805261.pdf&d=7QB4h8mQ1QBJp1iJ1m8od5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=f19bfd8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/fc/pwsc/results/v201805261.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年5月25日，林卓廷提出就「升降機維修保養對市民安全進行辯論議案」以6票之差未獲通過，7名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr1